>>REGINA MEREDITH: This
season on "Open Minds,"

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:18.380 align:middle line:84%
I've teamed up
with Freddy Silva,

00:00:18.380 --> 00:00:21.950 align:middle line:84%
author and world-renowned
expert on sacred sites.

00:00:21.950 --> 00:00:25.070 align:middle line:84%
Paola Harris, investigative
journalist and author

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:27.380 align:middle line:84%
in the field of
extraterrestrial-related

00:00:27.380 --> 00:00:28.550 align:middle line:90%
phenomena.

00:00:28.550 --> 00:00:34.310 align:middle line:84%
Local Sardinia guide Rosela
Loto, and Luigi Muscas,

00:00:34.310 --> 00:00:36.770 align:middle line:84%
a leading researcher
on giant bones

00:00:36.770 --> 00:00:39.980 align:middle line:84%
in Sardinia, who has
discovered evidence pointing

00:00:39.980 --> 00:00:43.280 align:middle line:84%
to the connection between
the island of Sardinia

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:47.030 align:middle line:84%
