island, revealing tombs, bones,

00:00:54.470 --> 00:00:57.110 align:middle line:84%
and highly sophisticated
architecture.

00:00:57.110 --> 00:00:59.690 align:middle line:84%
It's speculated that
people from Atlantis,

00:00:59.690 --> 00:01:02.360 align:middle line:84%
including a giant
race of people,

00:01:02.360 --> 00:01:05.269 align:middle line:84%
emigrated to Sardinia with
their great knowledge,

00:01:05.269 --> 00:01:09.320 align:middle line:84%
leaving their tombs and
temples called nuraghe behind.

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:11.690 align:middle line:10%
With help from a team
of remote viewers led

00:01:11.690 --> 00:01:14.480 align:middle line:10%
by Angela Thompson,
local Sardinia

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:17.540 align:middle line:10%
legends, and the writings
of Edgar Cayce and Ruth

00:01:17.540 --> 00:01:21.650 align:middle line:10%
Montgomery, we uncover a deeper
understanding of these giants,

00:01:21.650 --> 00:01:24.110 align:middle line:10%
their nuraghe, and the
mystery surrounding

00:01:24.110 --> 00:01:26.142 align:middle line:10%
their incredible
history on this island.

00:01:26.142 --> 00:01:28.100 align:middle line:84%
>>FREDDY SILVA: We're
taking little breadcrumbs

00:01:28.100 --> 00:01:30.080 align:middle line:84%
and trying to make a wonderful
loaf of bread out of it.

00:01:30.080 --> 00:01:31.580 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The message
that there may

00:01:31.580 --> 00:01:33.230 align:middle line:84%
have been highly
sophisticated cultures

00:01:33.230 --> 00:01:36.290 align:middle line:84%
before our current time
begs many questions

00:01:36.290 --> 00:01:37.850 align:middle line:90%
that we've been grappling with.

00:01:37.850 --> 00:01:39.620 align:middle line:90%
Why did they disappear?

00:01:39.620 --> 00:01:42.905 align:middle line:84%
And how many more are there
buried under the sands of time?

00:01:42.905 --> 00:01:48.190 align:middle line:90%


