And that's just with little
shards of tools, and so forth.

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:41.380 align:middle line:84%
And as it becomes
more sophisticated,

00:22:41.380 --> 00:22:43.600 align:middle line:84%
that's when we start looking
more toward modern time.

00:22:43.600 --> 00:22:48.160 align:middle line:84%
Well, not-- what they say
is 5,000 years ago, 4,000

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:49.768 align:middle line:90%
years ago, you're predating.

00:22:49.768 --> 00:22:51.310 align:middle line:84%
You're predating
that by quite a bit.

00:22:51.310 --> 00:22:54.790 align:middle line:84%
So relatively still modern
history after the great flood.

