00:37:06.420 --> 00:37:06.780 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:37:06.780 --> 00:37:08.713 align:middle line:84%
And so-- I mean, and
again, and this-- we're

00:37:08.713 --> 00:37:11.130 align:middle line:84%
going to get to this again
with the remote viewers in just

00:37:11.130 --> 00:37:13.020 align:middle line:90%
a minute with another location.

