But let's talk
about Santu Antine.

00:37:14.880 --> 00:37:17.010 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about
not the energy of it

00:37:17.010 --> 00:37:18.990 align:middle line:84%
that we experience, but
the actual alignments

00:37:18.990 --> 00:37:20.032 align:middle line:90%
and the structure itself.

