take your offspring

00:38:09.900 --> 00:38:12.390 align:middle line:84%
and make them into the
chiefs of Sardinia,

00:38:12.390 --> 00:38:14.160 align:middle line:84%
or whatever it was
called back then.

00:38:14.160 --> 00:38:16.860 align:middle line:84%
So we have this establishment
of a half-human, half-divine

00:38:16.860 --> 00:38:19.740 align:middle line:84%
bloodline from the myth
of Sardinia itself.

00:38:19.740 --> 00:38:21.480 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's a
primitive stairwell.

00:38:21.480 --> 00:38:23.650 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Yeah, that's a
very good observation.

