It has a double beehive
chamber, which is extraordinary.

00:38:58.620 --> 00:39:00.620 align:middle line:84%
I've never seen anything
quite like this before.

00:39:00.620 --> 00:39:03.200 align:middle line:84%
And at the bottom one you
have these four alcoves,

00:39:03.200 --> 00:39:05.240 align:middle line:84%
each one aligned to
the compass points,

00:39:05.240 --> 00:39:07.542 align:middle line:84%
as though some very
intellectual exercise

00:39:07.542 --> 00:39:08.750 align:middle line:90%
was being conducted in there.

00:39:08.750 --> 00:39:10.430 align:middle line:84%
That's the central
part of the site.

00:39:10.430 --> 00:39:12.230 align:middle line:84%
That's the original
part of the site.

00:39:12.230 --> 00:39:13.897 align:middle line:84%
Because if you stare
out of the doorway,

00:39:13.897 --> 00:39:15.890 align:middle line:84%
you're looking at a
blank wall and you think,

00:39:15.890 --> 00:39:18.020 align:middle line:84%
they would never have
done that because there's

